snippet.title: Best VGM 1400 - Donkey Kong Country Returns - Main Theme
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1037 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VZIA6ZoLBEA

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Main Theme
